44
00:10:56,870 --> 00:11:06,868
So I need to check the roots to cut off all damaged roots.

45
00:11:26,898 --> 00:11:36,896
Removing damaged roots helps prevent the rot from spreading, causing the entire root of the orchid to rot.

46
00:11:44,894 --> 00:11:54,892
