49
00:13:02,879 --> 00:13:12,877
Then add 1 teaspoon of Baking Soda to help kill bacteria and eliminate pests.

50
00:13:26,874 --> 00:13:36,872
Soak orchid roots in this water for 10 minutes.

51
00:13:56,868 --> 00:14:06,899
Then use dry moss to grow orchids.

52
00:14:09,899 --> 00:14:19,897
After soaking for 10 minutes, take the orchid out and plant it.

53
00:14:26,895 --> 00:14:36,893
